32#ifndef _LINUX_MATH64_H_
33#define _LINUX_MATH64_H_
34
35#include <sys/types.h>
36
37#include <asm/div64.h>
38
39static inline int64_t
40div64_u64(int64_t dividend, uint64_t divisor)
41{
42 return dividend / divisor;
43}
44
45static inline int64_t
46div_u64(int64_t dividend, uint32_t divisor)
47{
48 return dividend / divisor;
49}
50
51static inline int64_t
52div64_s64(int64_t dividend, int64_t divisor)
53{
54 return dividend / divisor;
55}
56
57static inline int64_t
58div_s64(int64_t dividend, int32_t divisor)
59{
60 return dividend / divisor;
61}
62
63static inline uint64_t
64div64_u64_rem(uint64_t dividend, uint64_t divisor, uint64_t *rem)
65{
66 *rem = dividend % divisor;
67 return dividend / divisor;
68}
69
70#endif /* _LINUX_MATH64_H_ */
